Globalstar Telecom GSTRF is a lightly traded stock th at gapped up Monday morning and moved steadily higher for the first half of the session before leveling off into a range The stock finished up by at on the highest volume in months Globalstar Telecom has b een trading in a range for the last months at the lows of the year but c limbed above resistance on Monday The stock also crossed its day movin g average for the first time in over a year The company announced today th at it will combine its lowearth orbit satellite constellation with Qualcom s QCOM digital technology to broadcast
